<p><span style="color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">郭名滦同学在会议上强调：“党的二十大是一次高举旗帜、凝聚力量、团结奋进的大会，为新时代新征程党和国家事业发展、实现第二个百年奋斗目标指明了前进方向、确立了行动指南。认真学习宣传贯彻党的二十大精神，事关党和国家事业继往开来，事关中国特色社会主义前途命运，事关中华民族伟大复兴。我辈应不忘初心，牢记使命。”</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEISQicX57ytHIIbBDEKgcTeWA1iaRAvfgQ8WTI3XI9RbEufpWIV5xbfJrBtQJibHWkQne5wOzuxM5xAw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="242" height="156" style="width: 242px; height: 156px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 245); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">学习好领悟好运用好“六个坚持”</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 245); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">坚持人民至上、坚持自立自信、</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 245); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none 0px !important; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text;">坚持</span>守正创新、坚持问题导向、</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 245); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">坚持系统观念、坚持胸怀天下、</strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(12, 12, 12); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 246, 245); max-inline-size: 100%; cursor: text; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); text-indent: 2em; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; outline: none 0px !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: transparent; font-family: 宋体;">深入学习贯彻党的二十大精神，把党的二十大作出的重大决策部署付诸行动、见之于成效，必须学懂弄通做实习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想，理解把握其世界观和方法论，坚持好、运用好贯穿其中的立场观点方法。这就要求我们在学习贯彻中深刻领会“六个坚持”，以理论武装头脑、指导实践、推动工作。</span></p><p><br/></p>